data.description: If you are looking for space, this is the home for you! This American classic home has been redesigned for today's living. Large room sizes with extra tall ceilings and plenty of windows give this home a light, bright, and open-concept feel! Features include 5 bedrooms, 3 baths in the main house, and a completely separate 1-bedroom guest suite with deck, screen porch, and separate entrance off the 2.5 car garage. This space is perfect for a Nanny, guest space, or multi-generational living! The main house has a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertop, hardwood floors throughout, and updated bathrooms. The laundry room, 1 bedroom, and full bath are all on the main level. The master suite with balcony overlooks the 300-foot-deep fenced lot and has a master bath with double sink, separate shower/ tub, and nice size sitting room. Enjoy sitting out on the deck that overlooks the large fenced backyard - Plenty of room to run and play! Unfinished basement with exterior access completes this home. Come take a look! Less than 1 mile to the Metra train. Downers Grove Schools, North HS. Schedule your showing today.
